model

Class Intersection

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Intersection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Agent, CarAcceptor

    public class Intersection
extends java.lang.Object
implements Agent, CarAcceptor
    The Intersection is a crossroads between to CarAcceptor Objects running North/South, and two CarAcceptor Objects running East/West. The Intersection contains a Light Object to control the visual changes to the intersection light.
    Author:
    Joseph Richard
